name: Dara
about:
I'm a freelancer, director and writer, based out of Chicago but wandering by professional necesity and personal choice. Books are the essential objects of my life. My mother's a librarian, my father's a professor, my brother's a scientist, and none of us goes anywhere without killing trees and ink vines.

I will say something about why ON BEAUTY is on my list of favorite books - it's the perfect tale of the academy.

name: Steven
about: Steven Tagle is a recent Stanford graduate who majored in English and psychology. His writing interests include: touring erotic museums, making sock puppets, and teaching robots to love. He works diligently to increase his Googleability, picks the vegetables out of his fried rice, and uses the excuse "I need to revise my play," to escape exercise and drunken parties. He is currently working on his first novel. Check him out at www.steventagle.com!
